DarkMouse::

She jumped up and stared at Quickstrike. "Quickstrike! It's you! By 
the matrix I thought you got scrapped or something!"
She was over joyed to see her old friend again. She stood up and gave 
him a hug. She then let go and sat back down. "Uh. sorry. I got a 
little carried away. But it's great to see you again commander." She 
was smiling broadly and her eyes were lit up as she looked at him.



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, wilddance_mare@h... wrote:
> Quickstrike:
> 
> Quickstrike lept into the transport pod with KitKat and the others, 
> immediately sitting down. The looked around for a moment, and 
noticed 
> a bot when he first jumped in. He turned his head and shoulders 
> around to see Dark Mouse. His optics lit up.
> 
> "Dark Mouse! That's where ya been. Ah thought ya got lost or 
> somethin'."
